OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1772917925
OL,3,CWhole-life term for man who murdered
OL,4,Cmum and three children in house fire
OL,6,FA man who murdered his ex-girlfriend's
OL,7,Fsister and her three children in a
OL,8,Fhouse fire has been given a rare whole-
OL,9,Flife sentence after being found guilty
OL,10,Fof their murders.
OL,12,FSharaz Ali, 40, killed Bryonie Gawith
OL,13,Fand her three children by setting fire
OL,14,Fto their house in Bradford in August
OL,15,F2024.
OL,17,FHis trial heard he had planned a
OL,18,Frevenge attack on Bryonie's sister,
OL,19,FAntonia Gawith, who was staying at the
OL,20,Fhouse, after she ended their
OL,21,Frelationship.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1772917925
OL,3,CWhole-life term for man who murdered
OL,4,Cmum and three children in house fire
OL,6,FSentencing Ali at Doncaster Crown
OL,7,FCourt, judge Mr Justice Hilliard KC
OL,8,Fsaid he was motivated by "revenge and
OL,9,Fsexual jealousy".
OL,11,F"It was part of a plan to wipe out a
OL,12,Fwhole family," he said.
OL,14,FThe sentence means Ali will never be
OL,15,Freleased from prison.
OL,17,FHis accomplice, Calum Sunderland, was
OL,18,Fjailed for life with a minimum 18-year
OL,19,Fterm after being convicted of
OL,20,Fmanslaughter.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1772917925
OL,3,CWhole-life term for man who murdered
OL,4,Cmum and three children in house fire
OL,6,F"No sentence I can pass can put right
OL,7,Fwhat the defendants have done," the
OL,8,Fjudge said. "That is not possible."
OL,10,F'Every breath has been a struggle'
OL,12,FIn a victim impact statement read in
OL,13,Fperson in court, Antonia Gawith said
OL,14,Fthe fire "shattered my entire
OL,15,Fexistence".
OL,17,F"What haunts me the most is the attack
OL,18,Fwas meant for me," she said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1772917925
OL,3,CWhole-life term for man who murdered
OL,4,Cmum and three children in house fire
OL,6,F"Petrol was poured on me (but) the
OL,7,Fviolence instead stole the life of my
OL,8,Fsister, Bryonie, my nieces, Denisty
OL,9,Fand Aubree Birtle, and my nephew,
OL,10,FOscar.
OL,12,F"The memories of seeing their lifeless
OL,13,Fbodies from the fire is etched on my
OL,14,Fmind with a permanence I cannot escape.
OL,16,F"Every breath since has been a
OL,17,Fstruggle to exist in a world that no
OL,18,Flonger feels safe or fair."
OL,26,@nD@ZpmnD@^pn
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1772917925
OL,3,CWhole-life term for man who murdered
OL,4,Cmum and three children in house fire
OL,6,FThe trial last year heard Ali planned
OL,7,Fthe attack after Antonia Gawith ended
OL,8,Fan abusive seven-year relationship
OL,9,Fwith him.
OL,11,FProsecutors said he was "motivated by
OL,12,Fjealousy and fuelled by drink and
OL,13,Fdrugs" when he torched the home on
OL,14,FWestbury Road in the early hours of 21
OL,15,FAugust 2024.
OL,17,FOn his way to her house, Ali texted
OL,18,FAntonia Gawith, using a misogynistic
OL,19,Fslur to describe her and Bryonie,
OL,20,Finsulted their mother and accused her
OL,21,Fof being with "some other man".
OL,26,@sD@YOUuD@FO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1772917925
OL,3,CWhole-life term for man who murdered
OL,4,Cmum and three children in house fire
OL,6,FWhile Antonia managed to escape the
OL,7,Ffire, Bryonie, 29, and her three
OL,8,Fchildren, Denisty Birtle, nine, Oscar
OL,9,FBirtle, five, and Aubree Birtle, 22
OL,10,Fmonths, were trapped upstairs.
OL,12,FAli, who suffered extensive burns and
OL,13,Fwas in a coma for several months, told
OL,14,Fthe trial that he wanted to kill
OL,15,Fhimself in front of Antonia, and only
OL,16,Fintended to set himself alight.
OL,18,FThe court heard he was rescued from
OL,19,Fthe fire by police who had arrived at
OL,20,Fthe scene first and initially refused
OL,21,Ftreatment.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1772917925
OL,3,CWhole-life term for man who murdered
OL,4,Cmum and three children in house fire
OL,6,FAli, who appeared in court in a
OL,7,Fwheelchair with a breathing tube, was
OL,8,Ffound guilty in December of murder and
OL,9,Fthe attempted murder of Antonia Gawith.
OL,11,FSunderland, 26, who went with Ali to
OL,12,Fthe house and kicked the door in for
OL,13,Fhim, was found guilty of manslaughter
OL,14,Fbut cleared of murder.
OL,16,FMohammed Shabir, who drove the pair to
OL,17,Fthe house, was due to go on trial with
OL,18,Fthem but died of a heart attack while
OL,19,Fon remand.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1772917925
OL,3,CWhole-life term for man who murdered
OL,4,Cmum and three children in house fire
OL,6,FIn a statement Bryonie Gawith's older
OL,7,Fsister, Clare Gawith, said she was "my
OL,8,Fbest friend and my right arm".
OL,10,F"Losing my sister, the person I
OL,11,Fthought I would grow old with, is a
OL,12,Fpain that follows me everywhere," she
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,FShe added: "When I finally drift off I
OL,16,Fwake up with nightmares."
OL,18,FSpeaking outside court after the
OL,19,Fhearing, Antonia Gawith described Ali
OL,20,Fand Sunderland as "monsters".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1772917925
OL,3,CWhole-life term for man who murdered
OL,4,Cmum and three children in house fire
OL,6,FShe added: "No sentence can bring back
OL,7,Ffour hearts that should still be
OL,8,Fbeating.
OL,10,F"Every day our hearts ache with
OL,11,Femptiness, every day we feel the
OL,12,Fweight of their absence, the joy we
OL,13,Flost, the moments that will never come.
OL,15,F"Every day we remember them, the love,
OL,16,Fthe light, the life they gave so
OL,17,Fbriefly, so beautifully.
OL,19,F"We carry them in every heart beat,
OL,20,Fevery tear, every memory, every act of
OL,21,Flove.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1772917925
OL,3,CWhole-life term for man who murdered
OL,4,Cmum and three children in house fire
OL,6,F"They live in us, they live through
OL,7,Fus, they will never be gone.
OL,9,F"Bryonie, Denisty, Oscar and Aubree
OL,10,Fyou are forever loved, forever ours,
OL,11,Fforever remembered, forever young."
OL,13,FAmanda McInnes, senior prosecutor for
OL,14,Fthe Crown Prosecution Service, said it
OL,15,Fwas "a devastating case in which a
OL,16,Fviolent man's jealousy led to the most
OL,17,Funimaginable consequences".
OL,19,FShe added: "Sharaz Ali showed no
OL,20,Fregard for the lives he destroyed that
OL,21,Fnight.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1772917925
OL,3,CWhole-life term for man who murdered
OL,4,Cmum and three children in house fire
OL,6,F"His former partner had made the
OL,7,Fcourageous decision to leave an
OL,8,Fabusive relationship, and his response
OL,9,Fwas to unleash a catastrophic act of
OL,10,Frevenge that killed four innocent
OL,11,Fpeople.
OL,13,F"Calum Sunderland willingly played his
OL,14,Fpart in this tragedy and it is right
OL,15,Fthat he too is held responsible for
OL,16,Fthe consequences of his actions."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
